cmake is needed. generate build dir as follows:

cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -G "CodeBlocks - Unix Makefiles" -S /home/vchari/ciis/programming_assigment_one -B /home/vchari/ciis/programming_assigment_one/DIRNAME

then run:

cmake --build /home/vchari/ciis/programming_assigment_one/DIRNAME --target programming_assigment_one